<div class="row">
    <div class="col-md-6">
        <h1 class="text-center">PRIVACY POLICY</h1>
        <h4 class="text-center">BATMAN'S GOT YOUR BACK</h4>

        <div class="privacy-policy-container">
            <h2>Batman:</h2>
            <p>I’m Batman. Welcome to Brick Haven, where we're committed to protecting your privacy with the same dedication as building the strongest LEGO structures. This Privacy Policy outlines how we collect, use, and safeguard your personal information, ensuring your trust and security in our digital LEGO world.</p>

            <h2>Data Collection: Assembling Information Blocks</h2>
            <p>Just as we piece together LEGO bricks to create masterpieces, we collect certain data to enhance your Brick Haven experience. This may include:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Personal Information: Your name, email address, and contact details, helping us communicate with you effectively and personalize your experience.</li>
                <li>Usage Data: Information about your interactions with our website or app, guiding us in improving our services and tailoring them to your needs.</li>
                <li>Device Information: Details about your device, such as IP address and browser type, ensuring optimal performance and security of our digital playground.</li>
            </ul>

            <h2>Data Usage: Constructing a Seamless Experience</h2>
            <p>We use the data we collect for the following purposes:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Providing Services: Delivering the LEGO sets and products you've ordered, just like building your dream creations brick by brick.</li>
                <li>Enhancing User Experience: Customizing our offerings to your preferences, ensuring an enjoyable and personalized journey through Brick Haven.</li>
                <li>Improving Security: Safeguarding your data from potential threats or unauthorized access, creating a secure haven for your information.</li>
                <li>Analyzing Performance: Evaluating the effectiveness of our website or app, so we can continuously refine and enhance your Brick Haven experience.</li>
            </ul>

            <h2>Data Protection: Fortifying the Brick Haven Walls</h2>
            <p>Rest assured, your data is as secure as the walls of a LEGO fortress. We implement industry-standard security measures to protect your information from unauthorized access, misuse, or alteration. Our digital stronghold is fortified with encryption, firewalls, and other advanced technologies to keep your data safe from intruders.</p>

            <h2>Data Sharing: Trusted Allies Only</h2>
            <p>We won't sell, rent, or trade your personal information to third parties—only the most trusted allies of Brick Haven have access. However, we may share your data with reliable partners or service providers who assist us in delivering our services, subject to strict confidentiality agreements.</p>

            <h2>Data Retention: Building Long-Lasting Foundations</h2>
            <p>We'll only retain your personal information for as long as necessary to fulfill the purposes outlined in this Privacy Policy, unless a longer retention period is required by law. Once our mission is complete, we'll securely dispose of or anonymize your data, ensuring a clean and organized Brick Haven.</p>

            <h2>Your Rights: Empowering the Builder</h2>
            <p>Just as master builders have control over their creations, you have certain rights regarding your personal data:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Access: You can request access to the personal information we hold about you and receive a copy of it.</li>
                <li>Correction: If any of your data is incorrect or incomplete, you can request corrections or updates.</li>
                <li>Deletion: You have the right to request the deletion of your personal information under certain circumstances.</li>
                <li>Objection: You can object to the processing of your data for certain purposes, such as direct marketing.</li>
                <li>Restriction: You have the right to restrict the processing of your data in certain situations.</li>
            </ul>
            <p>To exercise your rights or seek assistance with your privacy concerns, contact our Privacy Guardian, also known as our Chief Privacy Officer, using the contact details provided below.</p>

            <p>
                <strong>Brick Haven Privacy Guardian</strong><br>
                Address: 123 Brick Street, Brick Haven City<br>
                Email: privacy@brickhaven.com<br>
                Phone: +1 (555) BRK-HAVN
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>

